  "merger_description": "WPF Duratec Pty Ltd (WPF Duratec), a wholly owned subsidiary of Australian engineering, construction and remediation contractor Duratec Limited (Duratec) (ASX:DUR), proposes to acquire 100% of the shares in Davhold Australia Pty Ltd, trading as Pacific Welding Australia.\n\nDuratec is an Australian engineering, construction and remediation business. WPF Duratec is a specialist engineering, fabrication and site services provider based in Western Australia.\n\nPacific Welding Australia is an Australian welding and fabrication company based in Newcastle, New South Wales. Pacific Welding Australia specialises in the provision of project based welding, mechanical services and specialist fabrication to clients in the oil & gas, energy and mining industries.",
